145
00:09:49,669 --> 00:09:51,136
[ Dog barks ]

146
00:10:32,445 --> 00:10:34,345
[ Indistinct talking
and laughing ]

147
00:10:38,918 --> 00:10:40,010
Aw, what's his name?

148
00:10:40,086 --> 00:10:41,018
Doyle.

149
00:10:41,087 --> 00:10:42,486
Hi, Doyle.

150
00:11:08,581 --> 00:11:10,412
[ Indistinct talking ]

151
00:11:12,518 --> 00:11:13,815
I'm telling you,

152
