with you.

161
00:11:50,423 --> 00:11:52,914
Yeah. Okay.
Okay. We'll just be a minute.

162
00:11:52,992 --> 00:11:54,619
No dogs allowed
on the school grounds.

163
00:11:54,694 --> 00:11:56,457
Okay. Okay. I understand.

164
00:11:56,529 --> 00:11:58,724
Check this out.
Come here. He's all right.

165
00:11:58,798 --> 00:12:01,323
Look at what
a little punk I was.

166
00:12:05,571 --> 00:12:07,129
