could meet up somewhere.

233
00:14:42,094 --> 00:14:45,552
Maybe that place with the...
things that Frank goes to.

234
00:14:45,631 --> 00:14:46,893
And I'll find you later?

235
00:14:46,966 --> 00:14:47,898
Okay.

236
00:14:47,967 --> 00:14:49,025
- Yeah?
- Of course.

237
00:14:49,101 --> 00:14:50,090
All right.

238
00:14:52,438 --> 00:14:54,201
This one's cute
with the red shirt.

239
